<i>adverb</i>: 혹독히 [혹또키], 통렬히 [통ː녈히], 씁쓸히 [씁쓸히], 씁쓰레 [씁쓰레] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>혹독히 [혹또키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. harshly; severely; bitterly</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being excessively severe.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cruelly; mercilessly; harshly</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 하는 짓이 몹시 모질고 악하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of one's personality or actions being extremely wicked and heartless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>통렬히 [통ː녈히]</dt><br>
<dd>bitterly; bitingly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 강하고 날카롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very strongly and sharply.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>씁쓸히 [씁쓸히]</dt><br>
<dd>bitterly</dd><br>
<dd>싫거나 언짢은 기분으로.</dd><br>
<dd>With an unpleasant or bad feeling.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>씁쓰레 [씁쓰레]</dt><br>
<dd>bitterly</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 들지 않아 기분이 썩 좋지 않은 듯한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of feeling somewhat displeased because something is not to one's liking.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>